name: Artunist.ai x Tunes - First Edition Cover Art

metadata.name: The End Of An Identity
metadata.description: Artunist.ai x Tunes is a collaboration with the Tunes project to produce AI generated cover art for Tunes. The First Edition collection contains cover art in the style of the original Artunist.ai. Each cover is unique to its Tune and generated from the Tune's name without human intervention.
